

YOU WILL NEED A PLUGIN (ATLEAST THATS HOW IT IS IN INTELLIJ)
THE NAME OF THIS PLUGIN IS 'paste images as file'

1. select file in your file manager on your local system
2. copy file
3. go into your IDE and right-click on the directory you want to paste the file into
4. select paste (4th option from top)

this has been tested for .txt, .png and .pdf so far.